{"about_the_game":"Stellar Insurgency is a single-player, 3D, Open World, space game with rts and rpg elements. Explore a galaxy of 300 systems as you control your fleet in a top-down 3D style, navigating through Star-lanes, Warp gates, and Black holes. Customize and upgrade your fleet, complete missions, trade, hire your crew, wage war and determine the fate of the galaxy in this grand sim saga.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317550/extras/comet2.gif?t=1739263055\" /><br><br><strong>Major Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a galaxy of 300 systems controlling your fleet in a 3D top-down style.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Three playable Factions plus three additional. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cross the galaxy through Star-lanes, Warp gates and Black holes. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Customize and upgrade your fleet consisting from Fighters to Carriers and Battleships.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317550/extras/sp_customization.gif?t=1739263055\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Acquire techs via researching a well-structured tech tree.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Complete missions that impact your relations with galaxy\u2019s factions. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Forge alliances, wage war and determine the fate of the galaxy. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hire crew to improve the stats of your fleet. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Be a pirate (if you want to).</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Make profit through trade. </li></ul><br><strong>Minor Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore stellar objects through exploration probes. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Three levels of defense Stealth, Shields and Armor prior to component and hull damage. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use warp drive to jump locally and through solar systems.  <